{"id": "1417154671851606068", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "147364225411579904", "author_name": "strandiel", "content": "Quick CN related question, can anyone say if the translation of \"……果然是她。> ......It's her after all.\" can also be understood as \"...as expected of her\"/\"...as expected, it is her\"\n\nContext:\nKeeper: 第一次用就会群发广告了吗……这是从哪学来的……？\nDoresain: 那位叫詹金的孩子，对此处人心的洞察力令人印象深刻。\nKeeper: 詹金！\nKeeper:……果然是她。", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T14:26:43.230000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
{"id": "1417172523291770953", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "content": "yep, 果然 means \"as expected\" or \"sure enough\", and 是她 is \"is her\"", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T15:37:39.345000+00:00", "type": 19, "mentions": ["147364225411579904"], "reply_to": "1417154671851606068"}
{"id": "1417172636751888416", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "content": "so \"as expected of her\" is correct", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T15:38:06.396000+00:00"}
{"id": "1417172875475030077", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "content": "\"of course it'd be her\" is probably like the closest to how I immediately read it", "timestamp": "2025-09-15T15:39:03.312000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
